	abstract = {We present a full sky 100micron map that is a reprocessed composite of 
the COBE/DIRBE and IRAS/ISSA maps, with the zodiacal foreground and
confirmed point sources removed. We have constructed a map of the dust
temperature, so that the 100micron map can be converted to a map
